%% Vibook — Sequence diagram: business partner onboarding and admin approval

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Partner as Business Partner
    participant Mobile as Mobile App
    participant Profile as BusinessProfileController
    participant ProfileSvc as BusinessProfileService
    actor Admin as Platform Administrator
    participant AdminWeb as Admin Web SPA
    participant AdminCtrl as AdminBusinessProfileController
    participant AdminSvc as AdminBusinessProfileService
    participant Roles as BusinessUserRoleService
    participant Log as AdminActivityLogService
    participant DB as MySQL

    Note over Partner,DB: Partner applies — DRAFT to PENDING_REVIEW

    Partner->>Mobile: Complete business application form
    Mobile->>Profile: PUT /api/v1/business-profile/me
    Profile->>ProfileSvc: upsert profile (DRAFT)
    ProfileSvc->>DB: save business_profiles
    Profile-->>Mobile: BusinessProfileResponse

    Partner->>Mobile: Submit for review
    Mobile->>Profile: PATCH /api/v1/business-profile/me/submit
    Profile->>ProfileSvc: submitForReview()
    ProfileSvc->>DB: update status=PENDING_REVIEW
    Profile-->>Mobile: pending profile

    Note over Partner,DB: Admin approves — grant ROLE_BUSINESS

    Admin->>AdminWeb: Open pending business profiles queue
    AdminWeb->>AdminCtrl: GET /api/v1/admin/business-profiles?status=PENDING_REVIEW
    AdminCtrl->>DB: list profiles
    DB-->>AdminWeb: pending applications

    Admin->>AdminWeb: Approve application
    AdminWeb->>AdminCtrl: PATCH /api/v1/admin/business-profiles/{id}/approve
    AdminCtrl->>AdminSvc: approve(id)
    AdminSvc->>DB: update status=APPROVED, approvedAt
    AdminSvc->>Roles: grantBusinessRole(user)
    Roles->>DB: add ROLE_BUSINESS to user_roles
    AdminSvc->>Log: log APPROVE_BUSINESS_PROFILE
    Log->>DB: insert admin_activity_logs
    AdminSvc-->>AdminWeb: BusinessProfileResponse (APPROVED)
    AdminWeb-->>Admin: show success

    Note over Partner,DB: Approved partner can publish events

    Partner->>Mobile: Open partner hub
    Mobile->>Profile: GET /api/v1/business-profile/me
    Profile-->>Mobile: status=APPROVED
    Mobile-->>Partner: enable event management screens
